          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <ul class="flex items-center justify-between contrast-50">
            <li>
              - Full stack developer <span class="text-[#e61b38]">@Storyme</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <time datetime="2023-10">October 2023</time> - <time datetime="2024-01">January 2024</time>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="p-4">
            Worked with TypeScript and react on creating a Website builder
          </p>
        </div>
      </CardDescription>
    </Card>
  </CardWrapper>
</div>